  "description": "This technical note introduces the AIKernel Hash-Anchored Trust Layer (HATL), a hybrid trust architecture for Semantic Context Operating Systems. HATL separates high-frequency local commitments from lower-frequency public anchoring. Part I is the canonical English manuscript, Part II contains technical appendices and repository specifications, and Part III is the Japanese technical translation.",
